gambit is a 1966 comedy heist film starring shirley maclaine and michael caine as two criminals involved in an elaborate plot centered on a priceless antiquity from millionaire mr. &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , played by herbert lom . it was nominated for three academy awards . the film was advertised with the tagline , " go ahead : tell the end ( it 's too hilarious to keep secret ) but please do n't tell the beginning ! " gambit was directed by ronald neame from a screenplay by jack davies and alvin sargent from the original story of sidney carroll . a remake , with only basic ideas in common , was released in 2012 , with a script by joel and ethan coen .